Interface SampleType

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    SampleBoolean, SampleBooleanArray, SampleDouble, SampleDoubleArray, SampleDoubleArrayArray, SampleInt, SampleIntArray, SampleIntArrayArray, SampleLogDouble, SampleNewickTree, SampleString, SampleStringArray

    public interface SampleType
    Interface for data types that can be serialised for sampling. Implementing classes may e.g. provide convenience methods for serialisation (e.g. MCMC chain) and de-serialisation (e.g. chain parser).
